Solution
\series default
\color inherit
: This is essentially a Bernoulli model with 
\begin_inset Formula $mn$
\end_inset

 trials (the permutation part 
\begin_inset Formula $\left(\begin{array}{c}
m\\
x
\end{array}\right)$
\end_inset

