\begin_inset Formula $Beta(\alpha,\beta)$
\end_inset

 and the posterior is 
\begin_inset Formula $Beta(\alpha+\sum_{i=1}^{n}x_{i},\beta+nm-\sum_{i=1}^{n}x_{i})$
\end_inset

.
